high_descs: Turn left and walk to the doorway ahead and slightly to the left, entering the bedroom and approaching the sidetable on the right.
Pick up the knife from the bedstand.
Leave the lettuce the way you came in, then walk ahead and slightly to the right to the white table.
Cut up the lettuce on the table.
Look towards the far end of the diningtable.
Place the knife down on the diningtable.
Look back towards the diningtable.
Pick up the lettuce.
Walk left around the counters towards the kitchen area and go to the fridge.
Cool a piece of lettuce in the fridge and then remove the lettuce.
Return to the white diningtable you cut the lettuce on.
Place the lettuce on the end of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Place a cut up, cooled piece of Lettuce on a DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sidetable.
Take the knife from the side table.
Turn around and go to the lettuce on the table near the couch.
Cut the lettuce into pieces using the knife.
Turn right and go near the diningtable.
Put the knife on the corner of the diningtable.
Turn left and come near the diningtable.
Take the piece of lettuce from the table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the piece of lettuce into the refrigerator and cooled it.
Then take it out and go near the diningtable.
Put the lettuce on the corner of the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the piece of lettuce on the corner of the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn left to exit the kitchen and head to the bedroom across the passage and reach the sidetable.
Pick up the knife from the nightstand.
Head right to head out the room and reach the lettuce table.
Cut the lettuce on the table with the knife.
Turn right to face the diningtable.
Put the knife on the diningtable.
Move left to reach the cabbage on the diningtable.
Pick up the slice of lettuce from the table.
Head to the fridge on the left.
Cool the slice of lettuce in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to reach the white diningtable.
Put the slice of lettuce on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled slice of lettuce on the DiningTable.
